nodes.text: Dyspeth was a shadowy moon, that was located in the Varada sector of the Outer Rim.

Dyspeth was settled by a group of Human colonists in about 900 BBY in which they broke away from the Galactic Republic. A mysterious woman called Twilight united some of the Force-sensitive colonists to form the Disciples of Twilight, a Force-based organization that defended the population of the moon, but held no political or military power.
Dyspeth was rediscovered by a Republic survey team in about 500 BBY and the Disciples spread from the moon to nearby star systems.
